Global Plant Transformation Service Market Insights
Plant Transformation Service Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Plant Transformation Service Market Overview
The global plant transformation service market was valued at USD 6.7 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 11.2 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5%. This market growth is driven by the increasing demand for improved agricultural productivity, sustainable crop production, and the rising application of biotechnology in the agricultural industry. Plant transformation services, including gene editing and transgenic technology, play a critical role in producing crops with enhanced resistance to diseases, pests, and environmental stress. The market is influenced by both regulatory frameworks and technological advancements aimed at enhancing crop yields and addressing global food security challenges.

